The Lebanese interior minister said on Tuesday that initial indications showed that former Prime Minister Rafik Hariri was killed in a suicide car bombing . 
Hariri , 60 , a Sunni Muslim , resigned last October . 
Earlier in the day , Hariri was killed in a powerful explosion in the Lebanese capital of Beirut . 
He came to office first in 1992 and headed five governments over 12 years .
Hariri was known to be a friend of French President Jacques Chirac and had been to Washington to meet with President Bush on several occasions . 